'''Pad 642''' was a landing pad at [[Erwithat Spaceport]] on [[Pembric II]]. In [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], an [[Unidentified Aegis-class combat shuttle|''Aegis''-class combat shuttle]] assigned to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] ''[[FarStar]]'' utilized this pad when visiting Pembric II.

